each side has accused the other of interfering the united states 
says the soviet union is shipping arms to najibs government at the 
rate of 25 billion to 3 billion a year nearly double the figure 
before the withdrawal 
the united states has promised the guerrillas new weapons with 
which to disable airport runways and counter highaltitude bombing 
