free the territory beginning april 1 but on that date some 1000 
swapo guerrillas crossed into northern namibia from southern angola 
setting off three weeks of fighting that threatened to derail the 
independence plan 
but the peace process is back on track and swapo is favored to 
win preindependence elections in november 
