massive commitment of resources to law enforcement drug treatment 
programs drug education and more if that means raising taxes to 
pay for drugfighting measures so be it biden said tuesday we 
should not let the politics of readmylips stand in the way of a 
full scale effort to arrest the drug epidemic 
bennett told reporters tuesday that his plan will lay out terms 
of accountability for all aspects of this problem whether its the 
treatment side or the education side or the law enforcement side 
and were holding ourselves accountable 
were saying in 10 years theres going to be a lot less drug 
use said bennett 
